data.description: Just reduced , motivated seller ! This home has more room inside then it appears, This 2 bedroom,2 baths home is being sold as is with inspections encouraged.It has a large add on room with portable AC unit, a separate lanai, a sewing room with built ins to make the would- be seamstress happy. The metal roof was done 2019, Electrical panel replaced 2023. The one car garage has direct access to bathroom to gives that home mechanic easier access. The adjacent two carport is ideal to shade other projects.  The shed adds more storage in the large back yard. The location is walking distance to many shopping conveniences.
